<br />
Most of this self explains itself. <br />
<br />
The Free Peoples works nicely with mounts, and by the skirmish, most minions will be dead with just 1 more wound. Thinking of a copy of Éothain or two, dropping one Théoden and a copy of An Honorable Charge. Does anyone think that would work? He could get nasty at times. Same strength and one more vitality than Théoden...<br />
<br />
The Shadow try to get down a few minions, or as many as you can to wound or kill your oppnent, hurting them alittle at a time, until you kill them off before site 9. Usually it ends aruond 6-7, maybe alittle more, maybe alittle after. </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
